snippet.title: Arcane Quest Adventures Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Arcane Quest Adventures is a mobile RPG with original table top gameplay, faithful to the old board games like Hero Quest, Pathfinder and Dungeons and Dragons.

It's a spin off on the Arcane Quest series, introducing many new gameplay elements and an action mode to satisfy every player.

The game is available for FREE on all mobile platforms: Android, iOS and Windows Phone.
